946 _yes_err:QV=-(ERR=QE):QR(QV)=QR(QV)+1:GOSUB _output:ARGS QR$(QV)+"Error"+STR$(QE)+" in "+QA$
948 RESUME:ON ERROR GOTO 0:RETURN

